title: Acronis.True.Image.v8.0.791.Incl.Keygen
description:
Acronis True Image allows you to create an exact disk
image for complete system backup and disk cloning
providing the most comprehensive data protection.

The disk backup file contains the exact copy of a hard
disk, including all the computer data, operating
system, and programs.

After a system crash you can restore the entire system
or simply replace lost files and folders from your disk
backup.

Based on the exclusive Acronis Drive Snapshot disk
imaging technology, Acronis True Image allows you to
create an online system disk backup without reboot to
keep the system productive. The product provides the
fastest bare metal restore dramatically reducing a
downtime and your IT costs.
